Vitol Group bought 36,000 metric
tons of  jet fuel  from  Mangalore Refinery & Petrochemicals Ltd. (MRPL) ,
said three traders who declined to be identified because they
aren’t authorized to speak to the media.  Oil & Natural Gas Corp. (ONGC) , the country’s largest oil
producer, owns about 72 percent of Mangalore Refinery.  Details of the trade are as follow:  To contact the reporter on this story:
